ivardefs.name: approvalDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the asset content was approved by the publisher. Approval happens once when the content is officially approved for usage.

ivardefs.name: collection_
ivardefs.desc: The action to be performed for collecting the specimen.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: copyright
ivardefs.desc: Copyright statement relating to the SpecimenDefinition and/or its contents. Copyright statements are generally legal restrictions on the use and publishing of the SpecimenDefinition.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: For draft definitions, indicates the date of initial creation. For active definitions, represents the date of activation. For withdrawn definitions, indicates the date of withdrawal.

ivardefs.name: derivedFromCanonical_
ivardefs.desc: The canonical URL pointing to another FHIR-defined SpecimenDefinition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this definition.

ivardefs.name: derivedFromUri_
ivardefs.desc: The URL pointing to an externally-defined type of specimen, guideline or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this definition.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the SpecimenDefinition from the consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: effectivePeriod
ivardefs.desc: The period during which the SpecimenDefinition content was or is planned to be effective.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A flag to indicate that this SpecimenDefinition is not authored for  genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: A business identifier assigned to this SpecimenDefinition.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A jurisdiction in which the SpecimenDefinition is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: lastReviewDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the asset content was last reviewed. Review happens periodically after that, but doesn't change the original approval date.

ivardefs.name: patientPreparation_
ivardefs.desc: Preparation of the patient for specimen collection.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: Helps establish the "authority/credibility" of the SpecimenDefinition. May also allow for contact.

ivardefs.name: purpose
ivardefs.desc: Explains why this SpecimeDefinition is needed and why it has been designed as it has.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The current state of theSpecimenDefinition.

ivardefs.name: timeAspect
ivardefs.desc: Time aspect of specimen collection (duration or offset).

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the SpecimenDefinition.

ivardefs.name: typeCollected
ivardefs.desc: The kind of material to be collected.

ivardefs.name: typeTested_
ivardefs.desc: Specimen conditioned in a container as expected by the testing laboratory.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: An absolute URL that is used to identify this SpecimenDefinition when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance. This SHALL be a URL, SHOULD be globally unique, and SHOULD be an address at which this SpecimenDefinition is (or will

ivardefs.name: useContext_
ivardefs.desc: The content was developed with a focus and intent of supporting the contexts that are listed. These terms may be used to assist with indexing and searching of specimen definitions.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The identifier that is used to identify this version of the SpecimenDefinition when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or instance. This is an arbitrary value managed by the SpecimenDefinition author and is not expected to be globally uniq

properties.desc: A kind of specimen with associated set of requirements.
